## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1 — Database Models (Prisma Schema)

#### [MODIFY] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/z2k1s/OneDrive/Pictures/naj1/apps/api/prisma/schema.prisma)

إضافة 7 نماذج جديدة إلى نهاية الـ Schema:

1. **`PortalMessage`** — الرسائل بين المحامي والعميل
   - `id`, `organizationId`, `caseId?`, `senderId`, `senderType` (CLIENT/LAWYER), `content`, `messageType` (TEXT/FILE/VOICE), `fileUrl?`, `isRead`, `createdAt`
   - Relations: Organization, Client, Case

2. **`ClientAction`** — مركز الإجراءات المطلوبة (Action Center)
   - `id`, `organizationId`, `clientId`, `caseId?`, `actionType` (UPLOAD_DOCUMENT/SIGN_DOCUMENT/PAY_INVOICE/CONFIRM_HEARING/PROVIDE_INFO), `title`, `description?`, `status` (PENDING/COMPLETED/EXPIRED), `dueDate?`, `completedAt?`, `relatedEntityId?`, `createdAt`
   - Relations: Organization, Client, Case

3. **`PortalAppointment`** — حجز المواعيد
   - `id`, `organizationId`, `clientId`, `caseId?`, `appointmentType` (IN_PERSON/ZOOM/GOOGLE_MEET/TEAMS/PHONE), `title`, `scheduledAt`, `endAt`, `meetingUrl?`, `status` (REQUESTED/CONFIRMED/CANCELLED/COMPLETED), `notes?`, `createdAt`
   - Relations: Organization, Client, Case

4. **`PortalBranding`** — هوية بصرية للمكتب في البوابة
   - `id`, `organizationId` (unique), `logoUrl?`, `primaryColor`, `secondaryColor`, `fontFamily?`, `customDomain?`, `welcomeMessage?`
   - Relation: Organization

5. **`PortalPermission`** — صلاحيات العميل في البوابة
   - `id`, `organizationId`, `clientId`, `canViewCases`, `canViewDocuments`, `canViewInvoices`, `canUpload`, `canSign`, `canMessage`, `canViewNotes`, `canViewVerdict`, `canRequestAppointment`
   - Relations: Organization, Client

6. **`PortalAuditLog`** — سجل تدقيق البوابة
   - `id`, `organizationId`, `clientId`, `action` (LOGIN/VIEW_CASE/DOWNLOAD_DOC/UPLOAD_DOC/SIGN_DOC/SEND_MESSAGE/PAY_INVOICE), `entityType?`, `entityId?`, `ipAddress?`, `userAgent?`, `createdAt`
   - Relations: Organization, Client

7. **`CaseTimeline`** — مراحل القضية (Amazon-style tracking)
   - `id`, `organizationId`, `caseId`, `phase`, `title`, `description?`, `status` (COMPLETED/CURRENT/UPCOMING), `completedAt?`, `sortOrder`, `createdAt`
   - Relations: Organization, Case

إضافة enums جديدة:
- `PortalMessageType`: TEXT, FILE, VOICE
- `PortalSenderType`: CLIENT, LAWYER
- `ClientActionType`: UPLOAD_DOCUMENT, SIGN_DOCUMENT, PAY_INVOICE, CONFIRM_HEARING, PROVIDE_INFO
- `ClientActionStatus`: PENDING, COMPLETED, EXPIRED
- `PortalAppointmentType`: IN_PERSON, ZOOM, GOOGLE_MEET, TEAMS, PHONE
- `PortalAppointmentStatus`: REQUESTED, CONFIRMED, CANCELLED, COMPLETED
- `PortalAuditAction`: LOGIN, VIEW_CASE, DOWNLOAD_DOC, UPLOAD_DOC, SIGN_DOC, SEND_MESSAGE, PAY_INVOICE
- `CaseTimelineStatus`: COMPLETED, CURRENT, UPCOMING

تحديث الـ Relations في موديلات Organization, Client, Case لتشمل الحقول الجديدة.

